@startuml
[*] --> Satisfied

Satisfied --> Unsatisfied : Drive > Threshold

Unsatisfied --> Searching

Searching --> Engaging : Partner Found
Searching --> Searching : Partner Not Found

Engaging --> Engaging : Successful Exchange, Drive >= Threshold
Engaging --> Satisfied : Successful Exchange, Drive < Threshold
Engaging --> Searching : Unsuccessful Exchange

Satisfied --> Satisfied : Drive increments continuously
Unsatisfied --> Unsatisfied : Drive increments continuously
Searching --> Searching : Drive increments continuously
Engaging --> Engaging : Drive increments continuously

@enduml